title: Shoe’s on the other foot as Chinese company calls French sneaker firm ‘robbers’ for making Feiyue trainers
text:
Lifestyle › Fashion & Luxury Shoe’s on the other foot as Chinese company calls French sneaker firm ‘robbers’ for making Feiyue trainers 
Feiyue trainers are a durable make favoured by martial artists in China – and they’re also at the centre of an international dispute that raises questions about intellectual property in an age of global commerce PUBLISHED : Friday, 24 February, 2017, 6:01am UPDATED : Friday, 24 February, 2017, 6:01am
